<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMA522_03_SU_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css">

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_03_su.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_03_su_0002">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-type="2" data-text="생각 깨우기" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                  <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                    하준이는 인절미를 만드는 데 한 봉지에
                    <span class="mixed_fraction">
                        <span>1</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>1</span><span>5</span>
                        </span>
                    <span>
                    ㎞ 인 콩고물을 3봉지 사용했습니다. 인절미를 만드는 데 사용한 콩고물은 모두
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                    몇 ㎞ 인지 알아봅시다.
                  </div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents">
            <div class="input_area">
                <div class="img_row">
                    <div class="video_wrap">
                        <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_03_SU/0002_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="735" height="304" viewBox="0 0 735 304"
                            fill="none">
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="613" y="30.1875">1</tspan>
                            </text>
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="624.492" y="18.1875">1</tspan>
                            </text>
                            <line x1="623" y1="24" x2="633" y2="24" stroke="black" />
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="623.008" y="42.1875">4</tspan>
                            </text>
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="635" y="30.1875">㎞</tspan>
                            </text>
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="654" y="30.1875">씩 3봉지를</tspan>
                            </text>
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="621" y="62.1875">사용했으니까...</tspan>
                            </text>
                            <text fill="black" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-family="Pretendard"
                                font-size="16" letter-spacing="-0.5px">
                                <tspan x="52.8438" y="230.852">사용한 콩고물은
                                </tspan>
                                <tspan x="34.5781" y="254.852">모두 몇 ㎞인지 어떻게
                                </tspan>
                                <tspan x="60.8281" y="278.852">알 수 있을까?</tspan>
                            </text>
                        </svg>
                        <button class="play" data-video="1"></button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="input_area">
                        <h3 lang="y">
                            영상을 보고 사용한 콩고물의 양을 어떻게 구할 수 있을지 이야기해 보세요.
                        </h3>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <ol class="example_box">
                                <li lang="y"><span class="mixed_fraction">그림을 이용하여 구할 수 있습니다.</span></li>
                                <li lang="y">
                                    <span class="mixed_fraction">한 봉지에
                                        <span>1</span><span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>5</span></span>
                                        <span>㎞ 인 콩고물을 3봉지 사용했으므로</span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span class="mixed_fraction">
                                        <span>1</span><span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>5</span></span>
                                        <span>에 3을 곱해서 구할 수 있습니다.</span>
                                    </span>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <!-- 예시 필드에서 사용 -->
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset active">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit active">제출</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>